{"tha-ap416:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap416:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap416:0.3":"Madhumamsadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap416:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap416:1.2":"sukariko ahosaham; ","tha-ap416:1.3":"Ukkotakam randhayitva, ","tha-ap416:1.4":"madhumamsamhi okirim. ","tha-ap416:2.1":"Sannipatam aham gantva, ","tha-ap416:2.2":"ekam pattam gahesaham; ","tha-ap416:2.3":"Purayitvana tam pattam, ","tha-ap416:2.4":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham. ","tha-ap416:3.1":"Yottha therataro bhikkhu, ","tha-ap416:3.2":"niyyadesi mamam tada; ","tha-ap416:3.3":"Imina pattapurena, ","tha-ap416:3.4":"labhassu vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap416:4.1":"Duve sampattiyo bhutva, ","tha-ap416:4.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap416:4.3":"Pacchime vattamanamhi, ","tha-ap416:4.4":"kilese jhapayissati. ","tha-ap416:5.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap416:5.2":"tavatimsamagacchaham; ","tha-ap416:5.3":"Tattha bhutva pivitva ca, ","tha-ap416:5.4":"labhami vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap416:6.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap416:6.2":"pubbakammam anussarim; ","tha-ap416:6.3":"Annapanabhivasso me, ","tha-ap416:6.4":"abhivassati tavade. ","tha-ap416:7.1":"Idam pacchimakam mayham, ","tha-ap416:7.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","tha-ap416:7.3":"Idhapi annapanam me, ","tha-ap416:7.4":"vassate sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap416:8.1":"Teneva madhudanena, ","tha-ap416:8.2":"sandhavitva bhave aham; ","tha-ap416:8.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap416:8.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap416:9.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap416:9.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap416:9.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap416:9.4":"madhudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap416:10.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap416:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap416:10.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap416:11.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap416:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap416:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap416:12.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap416:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap416:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap416:13.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma madhumamsadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap416:14.1":"Madhumamsadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}